title: Rodgers’ Miracle & Week 13 preview
itunes:title: Rodgers’ Miracle & Week 13 preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – welcome back NFL Media’s Andrew Siciliano as they go game-by-game breaking down each Week 13 matchup. But first, the heroes recap the Packers unbelievable 37-23 victory over the Lions in a game that was sealed with a 61-yard Hail Mary pass from Aaron Rodgers to his second-year tight end Richard Rodgers.
